name: stardust_desmond_mulligan
notes: This is a transcription attempt for an excerpt (up to about ~4 min. in) of Hoagy Carmichael's 'Star Dust' as performed by Paul Desmond and Gerry Mulligan, from the album 'Two of a Mind'.
I think I got most of it but there are some bits that are still not quite right.
I've transcribed the solos for Bb trumpet so I can try playing them myself as a trumpet player :).
